{"tid":2315624,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【打倒巨人】136磅女拳手KO 528磅胖男　氣力被壓制靠「連環勾拳」86秒反勝","createTime":"2020-12-07T10:07:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T10:21:15.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2a4d1f0e1bf74433689298e92ceeffcd0272b23f","tid":2315624,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T10:07:45.000Z","msg":"身型比對手嬌小依然可戰勝對手！近日俄羅斯舉行了一場奇怪的MMA賽事，由一名136磅的女拳手，對戰528磅的業餘男掌手。在體重懸殊巨大的情況下，女拳手一直被壓制，但後面成功透過連環勾拳，於86秒反勝，KO 528磅的胖男！<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報道，Darina Mazdyuk是一名女MMA職業拳手，身高167cm、體重62公斤（136磅），臂展166公分，職業賽成績4勝1敗，主要在俄羅斯MMA賽事「Fight For Hype」155磅量級中出賽。<br />\n<br />\n而男選手Grigory Chistyakov則是一名網紅，在YouTube頻道上有近12萬人訂閱，身高181cm，體重240公斤（528磅），未曾在職業賽中出賽，算是業餘拳手。<br />\n<br />\n這場綜合格鬥（MMA）賽事由俄羅斯品牌「Наше Дело」（英譯︰Our Business）於上月底舉辦，當晚共有6場MMA比賽，當中五場都是正常賽事。<br />\n<br />\n從影片可見，Darina一開始處於下風，一直被有體型優勢的Grigory壓制，Grigory並利用推掌手段將Darina推向鐵籠。不過因二人僵持許久都沒有出招，裁判指示兩人分開，回到擂台中央繼續對戰。<br />\n<br />\n重新調整後，Darina先發動進攻，向Grigory的頭部使出勾拳，擊中面部後，再使出連續拳狂打頭部，使Grigory毫無還擊之力，抱頭跌倒。Darina Mazdyuk抓住機會連續攻擊，最後Grigory Chistyakov無法翻身應戰，只好投降。Darina用了86秒成功擊敗「巨人」。<br />\n<br />\n事後，身型肥胖Grigory Chistyakov表示最近身邊一名朋友的離世，促使他下定決心改善自己的健康。他在比賽後表示，「我將投入訓練，嘗試過更健康的生活。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2820000/2821874/0000_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2820000%2F2821874%2F0000_1024.png&h=9c59d920&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2820000/2821874/3_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2820000%2F2821874%2F3_1024.png&h=ecadea30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2820000/2821874/18_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2820000%2F2821874%2F18_1024.png&h=76628dc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sk9KXUoxGXw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fsk9KXUoxGXw&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTvYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=0326d7ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sk9KXUoxGXw</a>"},{"pid":"7c6e6aa5bd2071daa364d7bf7620bf8cc47d60f9","tid":2315624,"uid":47492,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T10:08:47.000Z","msg":"一睇就知假  同WWE一樣"},{"pid":"a988ff10827e8d2add41d6ab64219aea7028b7ab","tid":2315624,"uid":259010,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T10:09:57.000Z","msg":"戲黎姐"},{"pid":"cf67d2e248f6f865c6f115167dee8e641f431ab1","tid":2315624,"uid":203397,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T10:10:54.000Z","msg":"死豬咁訓撚左係地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24856111ca9403142e24b033e42c552a9c540518","tid":2315624,"uid":190789,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T10:11:09.000Z","msg":"肥佬d肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5966d6adf2fc31aeecc73ba9a48ba0c0112dc769","tid":2315624,"uid":275114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T10:13:23.000Z","msg":"個男人對波仲大過條囡"},{"pid":"f3b4279db7348115ad3ebd572ce125c885ac50d1","tid":2315624,"uid":279067,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T10:14:51.000Z","msg":"正常真係會輸左就任人踩仲可以對住鏡頭攞好pose影埋相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />假得濟"},{"pid":"6b8da64702657345a42d50f679d974ff58b21d7b","tid":2315624,"uid":148315,"like":0,"dislike":1,